an additional 8% of the options vest upon the completion of each of the next three periods of three months, an additional 9% of the options vest upon the completion of the next period of three months, and an additional 8% of the options vest upon
the completion of each of the next three periods of three months. Any unvested options vest immediately upon a change in control. 
