M.Eng degrees in Electrical Engineering from Cornell University. Our Board of Directors has concluded that Mr. YJ Kim should serve as a director based on his understanding of the Companys products and technology as our Chief Executive
Officer and his deep knowledge of the semiconductor industry. 
